<chapter id="support">
  <title>Community and Support</title>
  <section>
    <title>Building from the source </title>
    <para>You can fetch the latest version of the Sapo-Broker source code from our <ulink url="http://softwarelivre.sapo.pt/projects/broker/browser/trunk">subversion server</ulink>. For checking out the code use the svn command line client as follows:</para>
    <command>
      <prompt>svn co svn://softwarelivre.sapo.pt/broker/</prompt>
    </command>
    <para>To build, go to agents directory and type (you must have <ulink url="http://ant.apache.org/">ant</ulink> installed):</para>
    <command>
      <prompt>ant build-dist</prompt>
    </command>
  </section>
  <section>
    <title><anchor id="Howtogetinvolved"/>How to get involved</title>
    <para>Subscribe our mailing-list at <ulink url="http://listas.softwarelivre.sapo.pt/mailman/listinfo/broker">http://listas.softwarelivre.sapo.pt/mailman/listinfo/broker</ulink>.</para>
  </section>
  <section>
    <title><anchor id="publicbroker"/>Public broker</title>
    <para>If you want to play with available client libraries using a live Sapo-Broker agent you can use our public server. It's available at:</para>
    <screen>broker.labs.sapo.pt, TCP port 3322</screen>
    <para>Currently there is only an available public topic. Messages are published to this topic every time that a blog post is created, modified or removed from <ulink url="http://blogs.sapo.pt">Sapo Blogs</ulink> ('newpost','changedpost','removedpost'). Here is the topic name.</para>
    <screen>/sapo/blogs/activity/post</screen>
    <para>An example of a published content is presented.</para>
    <example>
      <title>Public agent notification sample</title>
      <screen>
&lt;notification xmlns="http://uri.sapo.pt/schemas/sapo/notification.xsd"&gt;
&lt;timestamp&gt;1169127665&lt;/timestamp&gt;
&lt;event&gt;
&lt;t:newpost xmlns:t="http://uri.sapo.pt/schemas/hpg/newpost.xsd"&gt;
   &lt;t:link&gt;http://chicailheu.blogs.sapo.pt/444615.html&lt;/t:link&gt;
   &lt;t:post_prop_taglist&gt;frases&lt;/t:post_prop_taglist>
   &lt;t:itemid&gt;1736&lt;/t:itemid&gt;
    &lt;t:post_prop_opt_preformatted&gt;1&lt;/t:post_prop_opt_preformatted&gt;
    &lt;t:new_date&gt;Thu Jan 18 13:41:05 2007&lt;/t:new_date&gt;
    &lt;t:subject&gt;Frase do dia&lt;/t:subject&gt;
    &lt;t:journalid&gt;3434&lt;/t:journalid&gt;
    &lt;t:post&gt;blablabla&lt;/t:post&gt;
    &lt;t:poster&gt;chicailheu&lt;/t:poster&gt;
    &lt;t:journal&gt;chicailheu&gt;/t:journal&gt;
&lt;/t:newpost&gt;
&lt;/event&gt;
&lt;/notification&gt;
      </screen>
    </example>

  </section>
